{"tid":827684,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"好掛住個ex","createTime":"2018-09-19T06:13:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-19T23:20:11.000Z","uid":66209,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"9da146b2930b4e7014502c646e936e3fc67929b2","tid":827684,"uid":66209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T06:13:32.000Z","msg":"之前成日為左佢上莊而嘈交<br />\n佢話好辛苦 但我都係愛佢同冇安全感姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我知係on9<br />\n但我知錯 我話我會改 佢話已經唔洗 之前唔信佢就冇<br />\n佢話如果我改 已經變左唔係當初佢鐘意個個 唔需要再改<br />\n覺得我地根本唔夾 一齊都冇意思 <br />\n但我真係好鐘意佢 佢都知我好鐘意佢 我陪佢共過患難<br />\n但係已經唔可以再一齊 <br />\n我求過佢 跪過佢 咩方法都試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我等佢飲完酒番黎 係佢樓下等左4,5個鐘 之後就同我講要分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而我每日見住佢由月頭同我嘈完交後係咁出去玩 我真係好唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好愛佢 唔想後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你見到可唔可以揾番我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 再試多最後一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71b13e88c2b08812d6e970f20163ea9e8fcb6e1c","tid":827684,"uid":151664,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T06:14:54.000Z","msg":"收嗲啦 你雞嚟咋"},{"pid":"4b232172ac778205f6a97a3c95f2ad44ccebaa02","tid":827684,"uid":200641,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T06:17:10.000Z","msg":"咁嘅理由都信<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇個款一早想飛你 等你開口咋"},{"pid":"5228ea2e5735380676fb23b23681a9b01a58422a","tid":827684,"uid":66209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71b13e88c2b08812d6e970f20163ea9e8fcb6e1c","tid":827684,"uid":151664,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"r